      "role": "user",
      "content": "the problem is that the revenue is actually still climbing despite the volatility. if i implement this cap, we're going to lose that extra margin. i've tried to look at the logs to see if there's a technical error, but the logs don't show any broken code, just these massive upward price shifts. i'm about to push the limit to production. is there any mathematical or data-driven reason why you'd suggest against it?",
